<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#f3fe59b257ff600aa804d08cfece45e1>.
<#f3fe59b257ff600aa804d08cfece45e1> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/bbcb137b-b8fc-450c-b67d-6c3239dbe0de>;
