<https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/c6ae10b6-6a18-4e15-9444-fbd746f4609d> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__426
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8d34170528a8b7045342cf19c418464d>.
<#8d34170528a8b7045342cf19c418464d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
