<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#2b125f9ab34409bdf143a8d1953b4e93>.
<#2b125f9ab34409bdf143a8d1953b4e93> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://doi.org/10.5878/bc12-w579>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-05-16T06:48:36.116Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#2b125f9ab34409bdf143a8d1953b4e93> {
<https://doi.org/10.5878/bc12-w579> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "passive remote sensing system"@en, "remote sensing data"@en, "Jordobservationsdata"@sv, "Earth observation data"@en, "LAND SURFACE"@en, "REFLECTANCE"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__44196.
_:b0__44196 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/principalInvestigator>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/402e6b92e1d5d3a426b2b63abdd311bb>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/bc12-w579> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021003211>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Optiska ’top of the atmosphere’ reflektans data från jordresurssatelliten Sentinel-2 för Uganda (2018-2020) laddades ner och processerades på ett systematiskt sätt till ’ bottom of the atmosphere’ reflektans med den öppna mjukvaran FORCE (Framework for Operational Radiometric Correction for Environmental monitoring, se https://force-eo.readthedocs.io/en/latest/). För varje år (2018-2020) beräknades antalet molnfria observationer och en bäst tillgänglig pixel mosaik skapades. För varje kvartal (12 totalt) beräknades f��r två vegetations index (EVI = Enhanced Vegetation Index och NDVI= Normalized Difference Vegetation Index) ett antal relevanta mått (minimum, maximum, medelvärde,standard avvikelse, 5%-, 50%- (median) och 95%-kvantiler). Data har 10 meters rumslig upplösning och är i GeoTIFF format.\nData är lämpliga för studier av framförallt vegetation och vegetationsförändringar. Mer information och detaljer i artikel publicerad i Data (https://www.mdpi.com/journal/data), 'submitted' 2021-02-15"@sv, "Optical top of the atmosphere reflectance data from the Earth resource satellite Sentinel-2 for Uganda (2018-2020) was downloaded and processed in a systematic way to bottom of the atmosphere reflectance with the open software FORCE (Framework for Operational Radiometric Correction for Environmental monitoring, see https://force-eo.readthedocs.io/en/latest/). For each year (2018-2020), the number of clear sky observations were calculated and a best available pixel mosaic were created. For each quarter (12 in total), for two vegetation indices (EVI = Enhanced Vegetation Index and NDVI = Normalized Difference Vegetation Index) a number of relevant measures were calculated (minimum, maximum, mean, standard deviation, 5%, 50% (median) and 95% quantiles). The data have 10-meter spatial resolution and are stored in GeoTIFF format. \nData are suitable for studies of vegetation and vegetation changes. More information and details in article published in Data (https://www.mdpi.com/journal/data), 'submitted' 2021-02-15"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/226074>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/3a00800ac30b03b7160876e65e1eaab1>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/bc12-w579#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2021-03-29T15:00:09.163921Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/bc12-w579>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2023-09-15T07:41:40.273777Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Sentinel-2 data för Uganda"@sv, "Sentinel-2 Data set for Uganda"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__68391.
_:b0__68391 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2020-12-31"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
