<#7b34f0ece6eee22a3ad3528c0bc7811d> {
<https://doi.org/10.5878/002061> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__50477.
_:b0__50477 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#hadRole> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/ResponsiblePartyRole/author>;
