<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#89d5725b6d4b97e7037c038671c4faae>.
<#89d5725b6d4b97e7037c038671c4faae> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://metadata.trafikverket.se/store/1/resource/186>;
